data.description: Welcome to 20819 Westfield Grove Place! This gorgeous single story home in coveted Katy, TX  is one of the largest in the neighborhood. This home offers multitude of upgrades.     Soaring high ceilings , recessed lighting, huge chefs kitchen and open floor plan is everything modern buyer is looking for.     Split bedroom location allows for privacy.     Wonderful surprise is the Bonus Room, located just of the main living area. This space  can be a Game room, Home Office , Man Cave, Home Gym - possibilities are endless!    Make your appointment to view today!  All room sizes are approximate. Please verify the room sizes and school information independently.
